# COMMON BEGINNER ERRORS

# 1. Confusing `end()`

`end()` points AFTER last element.

---

# 2. Dereferencing Invalid Iterator

Dangerous.

---

# 3. Copying Large Objects Accidentally

Use references.

---

# 4. Forgetting `auto&`

Performance issue.

---

# 5. Vector Index Out of Bounds

Undefined behavior.

